### 1. Valid expense under $100 (Auto-approved)
POST http://localhost:7071/api/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employee_name": "John Doe",
  "employee_email": "john@example.com",
  "amount": 50,
  "category": "meals",
  "description": "Lunch meeting",
  "manager_email": "manager@example.com"
}

### 2. Valid expense >= $100, manager approves
POST http://localhost:7071/api/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employee_name": "Jane Doe",
  "employee_email": "jane@example.com",
  "amount": 200,
  "category": "travel",
  "description": "Flight ticket",
  "manager_email": "manager@example.com"
}
### Copy the "id" from response, then:
POST http://localhost:7071/api/manager-response?instanceId=603f6ee3fa7845d593dcd56d91de7482&approved=true

### Check result:
GET http://localhost:7071/runtime/webhooks/durabletask/instances/603f6ee3fa7845d593dcd56d91de7482

### 3. Valid expense >= $100, manager rejects
POST http://localhost:7071/api/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employee_name": "Bob Smith",
  "employee_email": "bob@example.com",
  "amount": 300,
  "category": "equipment",
  "description": "Laptop purchase",
  "manager_email": "manager@example.com"
}

### Copy the "id" from response, then:
POST http://localhost:7071/api/manager-response?instanceId=0609ee24358b4b508086e1b0d6a4af16&approved=false

### Check result:
GET http://localhost:7071/runtime/webhooks/durabletask/instances/0609ee24358b4b508086e1b0d6a4af16


### 4. Valid expense >= $100, no manager response
# Do nothing → wait ~30 seconds → Escalated

###

### 5. Missing required fields
POST http://localhost:7071/api/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employee_name": "Alice"
}

###

### 6. Invalid category
POST http://localhost:7071/api/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employee_name": "Alice",
  "employee_email": "alice@example.com",
  "amount": 150,
  "category": "gaming",
  "description": "Console",
  "manager_email": "manager@example.com"
}